{"tid":1469894,"cid":33,"subCid":0,"title":"唔入黎睇嘅你 不配做連登仔","createTime":"2019-08-14T03:29:34.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-14T03:55:11.000Z","uid":63667,"like":13,"dislike":5,"uniUserReply":9,"replies":[{"pid":"c36fa33f1fdf1f6230c1c36cdfab05d1fdc6b9c4","tid":1469894,"uid":63667,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-14T03:29:34.000Z","msg":"大家自己睇 點解機場一事會咁大迴響？<br />\n連登應該有共識知道<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">打記者同FA係黑警臥底</span></span><br />\n點解會有一堆失敗論同埋分化撚？<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">因為機場影響真係好大</span></span><br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">因為三毛取代連登仔做主導</span></span><br />\n<br />\n點解仲有人會不斷係度指責？<br />\n明知係對方嘅分化策略<br />\n就係想阻止你地影響機場<br />\n出埋禁制令更加明顯<br />\n就係要令大家轉移目標<br />\n<br />\n希望大家見到 真係要人手置頂<br />\n如果呢個post好快沉<br />\n一係連登仔已經被三毛風向帶走<br />\n一係連登已經唔係連登仔主導<br />\n<br />\n如果呢種事實 連登仔連入黎推一下都懶<br />\n結果不言而喻<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7baea540f89ad559300899d7cc22ec357baddeb6","tid":1469894,"uid":63667,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-14T03:30:22.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f4b191b256316c489812d1da59d47f868b112a26","tid":1469894,"uid":63667,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-14T03:31:25.000Z","msg":"認真post無人睇<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f64592525a69456e5a6d9a704d8ef6b3bea88b3e","tid":1469894,"uid":238367,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-14T03:31:52.000Z","msg":"幫你推一推"},{"pid":"7b163a2e4c453f3d1c59ea6d2c02cbcfcd3f23bf","tid":1469894,"uid":63667,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"f64592525a69456e5a6d9a704d8ef6b3bea88b3e","tid":1469894,"uid":238367,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-14T03:31:52.000Z","msg":"幫你推一推"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-14T03